msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_texturerect.rst:19
msgid ""
"Used to draw icons and sprites in a user interface. The texture's "
"placement can be controlled with the :ref:`stretch_mode "
"<class_TextureRect_property_stretch_mode>` property. It can scale, tile, "
"or stay centered inside its bounding rectangle."
msgstr ""
"用于在用户界面中绘制图标和精灵。纹理的位置可以通过 :ref:`stretch_mode "
"<class_TextureRect_property_stretch_mode>` 属性来控制。它可以缩放、平铺或保持居中于其边界矩形内。"

